**43.** If a certain principal amounts to Tk. $460$ (with interest) in $3$ years and to Tk. $500$ (with interest) in $5$ years, what will be the annual interest rate?<br>
[Directorate of Technical Education (Chief Assistant/Accountant)-2021] + [PKSF (AM)-2023]

